<li><a href="/scp-1053">SCP-1053</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-2543">SCP-2543</a></li>
</ul>

    
    
    
    </div>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">SCP Files Updated By The World’s Youngest Glacier</span>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-419">SCP-419</a></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Documents Filed by Goldsheiner</span>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/follow-the-keter">Follow the Keter</a></li>
<li><a href="/placere-non-trinus">Placere Non Trinus</a></li>
<li><a href="/rising">Rising</a></li>
<li><a href="/freaky-commodities">Freaky Commodities</a></li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p>Goldsheiner's <a href="http://scpsandboxwiki.wikidot.com/reject-s-sandbox">old</a> <a href="http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/reject">desk</a> has yet to be cleaned because something smells like toothpaste in there.</p>
<hr />
<p>&quot;That damn new-fangled computery thingum stuff.&quot;</p>
